  Notify["Notify through dashboard / alert"]:::external

  Probe --> Endpoint --> Dependencies
  Dependencies -- Yes --> Healthy
  Dependencies -- No --> Unhealthy --> Restart --> Probe
  Restart -. repeated failure .-> Reschedule --> Notify
